Reasoning: The paper discusses the integration of power domain NOMA with various communication technologies and optimization methods to maximize achievable rates. This topic falls under the broad category of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses coordinated multi-point transmission and reception, which falls under the category of communication systems (cs.COMM). The use of massive MIMO and millimeter wave communications falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the use of UAV-assisted communications, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
